race.comment: HIGH TOR (11) continues to race well and looks the one to beat. Easy winner two back then got home hard and was runner-up latest. Drawn for a soft run and looks tough to beat again. RAMBLING (12) is lightly raced and absolutely bolted in with her maiden win last time at Jamestown. Drawn well here and with the confidence from the win can measure up again. HOT OFF (5) finished alongside EXOTIC DANCER when well back last time. Mixing form but like her finds an easier assignment and give another go. LASTAR (2) returned from a long spell with a win in a similar class at Balaklava. Fitter again and is right in the mix. Something for the Multiples: TESTA DEXTA (8)
